**Historieta, cómic o tebeo: 2020 is the year of** comics!
On this occasion, the Collex Etudes Ibériques proposes a presentation of works from its collections.
The accompanying bibliography covers a large part of the history of the Spanish comic book: its influences, its relationship to history, literature but also its social and political dimension....
The presentation is illustrated by albums belonging to:
- at the Institut Cervantes in Toulouse, from 29 January to 29 February 2020;
- at the Ut2jvd Language Resource Centre from 2 March to 3 April 2020;
